      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA WHISKEY (1) is better than last start when fourth (27.80) in a Restricted WIN at Horsham over 485m. Form here excellent including two wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. WEBLEC MEMPHIS (7) showed strong early pace and stuck on well despite finishing out of the placings when fourth over 515m this track in 30.01. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Shapes as one to consider. PAW WELKES (3) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.93) at this track behind Moraine Sara in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature again.",
